r=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xsr1665703532612.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xsr1665703532612.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xsr1665703532612.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xsr1665703532612\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Send messages to\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specify where messages are sent if the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$PUTMESS_LOG_FILE</span> assignment setting is not specified.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xsr1665703532612__section_w1436ab1b5b1_w1437ab1b5_w1438ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"xsr1665703532612__table_d18527e1_d18528e1_d18529e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xsr1665703532612__table_d18527e1_d18528e1_d18529e1__entry__1\">\n Option\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xsr1665703532612__table_d18527e1_d18528e1_d18529e1__entry__2\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xsr1665703532612__table_d18527e1_d18528e1_d18529e1__entry__1\">\n Message Frame\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xsr1665703532612__table_d18527e1_d18528e1_d18529e1__entry__2\">\n Send messages to the application's message frame.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xsr1665703532612__table_d18527e1_d18528e1_d18529e1__entry__1\">\n Transcript Window\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xsr1665703532612__table_d18527e1_d18528e1_d18529e1__entry__2\">\n Send messages to the application's transcript window.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xsr1665703532612__section_pzk_snh_tcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d383956e100\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xsr1665703532612__p_d175883e1_d175884e1_d175885e1\">If the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$PUTMESS_LOG_FILE</span>\n            assignment setting is specified, all messages are always sent to both the message frame\n            and the defined log file. Use this setting to determine what happens if it is not\n            specified.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zea1665702607771.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$PUTMESS_LOG_FILE</a><p>Copy the message frame contents to one or more files.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8424121\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8424121\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Send messages to Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 17, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Send messages to Specify where messages are sent if the $PUTMESS_LOG_FILE assignment setting is not specified. Option Description Message Frame Send messages to the application's message frame. Transcript Window Send messages to the application's transcript window. Description If the $PUTMESS_LOG_FILE assignment setting is specified, all messages are always sent to both the message frame and the defined log file. Use this setting to determine what happens if it is not specified. Related Links $PUTMESS_LOG_FILE Copy the message frame contents to one or more files. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}